    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不同寻常的国际象棋规则——无需任何先验知识！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个版本的国际象棋中，棋子不会立即互相消灭，因此小失误的惩罚较小。棋子有生命值，必须通过攻击将其耗尽才会被淘汰。你可以治疗你的部队来保证他们的生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/e3acbcd3e0f97fb793c31645bb2327f9.poster.avif?t=1769026812\" aria-label=\"Gif showing knight chess pieces jumping arround and fighting a giant pawn.\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/e3acbcd3e0f97fb793c31645bb2327f9.webm?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/e3acbcd3e0f97fb793c31645bb2327f9.mp4?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你只需移动棋子——剩下的都由系统自动完成！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以控制单位的移动，它们会在条件允许时自动攻击对手。如果满足特定条件，单位还会尝试自动治疗自身。例如，主教可以治疗斜对角线上的棋子，而兵在移动时会治疗自身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/4e368ccaee2ff331d5c61e7f926538dc.poster.avif?t=1769026812\" aria-label=\"Gif showing a upgrade menu, the player leveled up.\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/4e368ccaee2ff331d5c61e7f926538dc.webm?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/4e368ccaee2ff331d5c61e7f926538dc.mp4?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >给你的部队装备武器和盔甲，提升等级！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找宝藏，掠夺强力武器，分配给你的角色，提升他们的生命值和力量。一路上，你还可以招募更多棋子加入你的队伍。选择能够完美配合的单位，最大化队伍的实力。随着等级提升，升级你的单位和法术。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的王位之路！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋盘清空后，你可以选择下一步的路线。你可以选择避开难度较高的棋盘，或者或许更艰巨的挑战也值得你付出努力？深入城堡，你将遭遇怪物、巨人和首领。你能否一路过关斩将，最终成为新的统治者？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/0a32bbd631eafc1f7fb628c4ca614102.poster.avif?t=1769026812\" aria-label=\"Gif showing the player choosing between two paths which will decide which chessboard the player faces next.\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/0a32bbd631eafc1f7fb628c4ca614102.webm?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210650/extras/0a32bbd631eafc1f7fb628c4ca614102.mp4?t=1769026812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
